</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/udrutt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drutt</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/6/01 6:32:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=563.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: More Grouping W/ Weirdos Fun</span><hr size=1> This whole &quot;must have this and must have that&quot; mentallity comes from the fact that EQ is aimed at uberquest, the high end, the big encounters.<br>
<br>
In uberquest you only need one of each buff/utility class, and a ton of wars, rogues and clerics. Banespells and trueshot gave lvl 60 wizards and 55+ rangers a useful role, but that didn´t change much. As long as the game is focused on uberquest, rangers are not supposed to tank. Necros are manafeeders and DMF. Magicians are CoTH, preferably on opposite faction. And so on.<br>
Perhaps a ranger or even Edeinas pet can tank frogs in Sebilis, but people will still want a warrior. He does the job better, and everyone knows the Big Guild has warriors tanking everything.<br>
<br>
Trakanon is outdated just like the rest of Sebilis. On 32k mobs who needs a main tank? It´s just a matter of killing the mofo before the second AoE. Velious -&gt; increased HP -&gt; more power to the three key classes.<br>
Maybe, if Verant decided to create let´s say 20k mobs with some insane spells, there would become a shift in the balance between classes in uberquest. But 20k mobs could be zerged, if you had enough of...the three key classes. So that won´t happend.<br>
<br>
Bottom line is, the prejudice about classes is based on the high end game. That´s where people are aiming. Therefor they want a warrior, even in Sebilis. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uzangal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zangal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(11/6/01 6:39:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=563.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: More Grouping W/ Weirdos Fun</span><hr size=1> Look for me...<br>
